        "## SQL Analysis\n",
        "Need to calculate the following:\n",
        "- Pass Rate = (Students Passed / Total Students)* 100\n",
        "- Failure Rate = (Students Failed / Total Students) * 100\n",
        "- Program Pass Rate = (Program Passes / Program Enrollments) * 100\n",
        "- Program Failure Rate = (Program Fails / Program Enrollments) * 100\n",
        "- Instructor Pass Rate = (Students Passed / Students Taught) * 100\n",
        "- Instructor Failure Rate = (Students Failed / Students Taught) * 100\n",
        "- Course Pass Rate = (Passes / Enrollemts) * 100\n",
        "- Course Failure Rate = (Failures / Enrollments) * 100\n",
        "- Retention Rate = (Students Returning / Students in Original Cohort) * 100\n",
        "- At-Risk Rate = (At-Risk Students / Total Students) * 100\n",
        "- High-Risk Rate = (High-Risk Students / Total Students) * 100\n"
      ],
